In the future, when funds and/or time allows us to, we possibly could add these features too (however, these may change!):<ul><li>Your own private gallery for screenshots &amp; photos</li><li>Your own @erollisimarr.com email address for web based email</li><li>CGI IRC chat for those who want to chat with friends while being at work but can't because of a firewall blocking the ports</li></ul>Or suggest a feature.<br />
<br />
What not to expect: being a supporter won't give you a wildcard or anything like that. You will be treated like everyone else, meaning that our forum rules still apply.<br />
